<br>
WTF?  You saying a self-only buff doesn't count as spending money on the group?  Isn't someone casting self-only buff STILL a member of the group and contributing in some way to the group action?  What about the other group buffs that other classes use as well?  Not to mention a self-buffer using their own peridots is not getting buffed by the cleric asking for reimbursement.<br>
<br>
Paladins use symbol spells that require reagents too... never seen them asking for all the gems or any special compensation.<br>
Enchanters use reagents including peridots for their Rune spells.  When do they get special loot splits?<br>
All higher level &quot;kill shot&quot; spells including wizzie bane spells use reagents.  In fact banes use 2 peridots per cast.<br>
Wizzie, as I mention alrdy, use peridots for manaskin.  Without it we are dead, or the cleric can use precious mana healing us when they should be healing the tanks.<br>
In an AoE group in Seb I can guarantee the wizzies go thru a hundred of them on manaskin while the single cleric uses hardly any doing their job of keeping the enchanters alive.  Yet nobody asks for special loot splits in AoE.. the gems and everything else are split normally.<br>
<br>
FYI - My cleric friend made 6,500K on his gem cleanout.  That was after about 2 months of playing, and not all of it was spent in OS getting gems.  He loves the gem-split rule the way it is and you can see why.<br>
<br>
Bring on the pay-as-you-go rule.  Let people use a precious slot in their inventory and bring their own peridots for Symbols and Aego. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ucaladdor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caladdor</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://wwp.icq.com/scripts/online.dll?icq=9311062&img=5 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 463<br> <font color=#E9D756>(7/28/01 7:26:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: clerics peridots and you </span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Whats that retarded &quot;kaboom&quot; sound effect ? <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
